definitions.definition: A small village and civil parish in Telford and Wrekin district, Shropshire , England ( OS grid ref SJ7321 ) .
A district municipality in north-eastern British Columbia , Canada .
An unincorporated community in Morgan County , Indiana , United States .
A small inland town in Victoria , Australia .
